    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the chilling world of <i>Hidden Evil</i>, where survival is your only goal. Trapped inside a mysterious house, you must explore every dark corner to uncover hidden items that hold the key to your escape. But beware—you're not alone. Sinister creatures lurk outside, desperate to break in and claim their prey. Your only defense? A powerful UV light that can hold them at bay—if you’re fast enough. Can you outsmart the horrors within and escape before it’s too late? Your courage, strategy, and reflexes will be put to the ultimate test. Good luck—you’ll need it.</p>",
